00:08:44.320 --> 00:08:45.320
Here,

00:08:45.800 --> 00:08:47.400
you could be my right hand.

00:08:48.119 --> 00:08:48.719
Zhixia.

00:08:49.280 --> 00:08:50.349
You're so capable.

00:08:50.350 --> 00:08:52.871
