Everyone around here knows.

00:37:09.720 --> 00:37:10.679
I tell you,

00:37:11.079 --> 00:37:13.119
back then, in Yujia Village,

00:37:13.119 --> 00:37:14.880
there was a village hospital.

00:37:14.999 --> 00:37:16.840
A family had twins,

00:37:16.840 --> 00:37:17.960
but couldn't afford both.

00:37:18.119 --> 00:37:19.469
The boy was kept,

00:37:19.470 --> 00:37:21.182
and the girl was sent
to the Shen family.

00:37:24.199 --> 00:37:26.920
That family really was harsh.

00:37:27.119 --> 00:37:28.639
Not really fair to say that.

00:37:28.639 --> 00:37:30.920
They sent her because
the Shen family was good.

00:37:31.280 --> 00:37:33.159
After all these years,

00:37:33.199 --> 00:37:35.400
the old Shen couple
treats their daughter

00:37:35.400 --> 00:37:36.999
even better than their biological son.

00:37:37.199 --> 00:37:38.720
When Mingzhu learned piano as a kid,

00:37:38.880 --> 00:37:40.360
they spared no expense.

00:37:40.360 --> 00:37:41.880
Minghui wanted a basketball,

00:37:41.880 --> 00:37:43.119
but they didn't agree.

00:37:45.400 --> 00:37:46.039
That...

00:37:46.039 --> 00:37:47.920
This girl's life is pretty good.

00:37:47.999 --> 00:37:49.199
Very good.

00:37:50.400 --> 00:37:51.039
Not really.

00:37:51.039 --> 00:37:52.119
Her husband's dead.

00:37:54.159 --> 00:37:55.999
Check out other things.

00:37:56.479 --> 00:37:57.039
No need.

00:37:57.039 --> 00:37:58.440
How much is it in total?

00:37:58.440 --> 00:37:59.639
Alright, let me calculate.

00:37:59.639 --> 00:38:00.360
Two boxes.

00:38:01.840 --> 00:38:02.800
Total 396 yuan.

00:38:05.720 --> 00:38:07.519
What's going on?
The kid's still not back.

00:38:07.519 --> 00:38:09.400
Stay calm.

00:38:13.880 --> 00:38:15.360
Zhixia is back.

00:38:15.360 --> 00:38:16.382
Zhixia, how's it going?

00:38:16.440 --> 00:38:17.320
What happened?

00:38:17.320 --> 00:38:18.199
Yes, yes.

00:38:18.880 --> 00:38:20.599
First, pay for the milk powder.

00:38:20.599 --> 00:38:21.599
Three ninety-six yuan.

00:38:21.599 --> 00:38:22.679
Round up to 400 yuan.

00:38:22.804 --> 00:38:23.550
Five hundred yuan.

00:38:23.720 --> 00:38:24.440
Okay, 500 yuan.

00:38:24.440 --> 00:38:26.320
I'll transfer five hundred yuan
to you shortly.

00:38:26.440 --> 00:38:27.639
You're starting to extort.

00:38:27.760 --> 00:38:29.493
Mom and Dad are so easy
to deal with now.

00:38:29.493 --> 00:38:30.648
Then why don't you do it?

00:38:30.671 --> 00:38:31.790
I don't have startup capital.

00:38:31.804 --> 00:38:32.999
Go away. Stop talking.

00:38:33.840 --> 00:38:34.519
Zhixia.

00:38:34.519 --> 00:38:35.079
Yes.

00:38:35.159 --> 00:38:36.440
Have you met her in person?

00:38:36.440 --> 00:38:37.079
Yes.

00:38:38.199 --> 00:38:39.880
Not the real person yet.

00:38:40.400 --> 00:38:41.960
But I met her parents.

00:38:42.079 --> 00:38:43.479
The couple was quite polite.

00:38:43.559 --> 00:38:45.159
They run a small restaurant.

00:38:45.159 --> 00:38:45.999
Business is good.

00:38:45.999 --> 00:38:47.559
Mostly serving locals.

00:38:47.559 --> 00:38:48.159
Right.

00:38:48.559 --> 00:38:51.079
Zhilu is my daughter.

00:38:51.400 --> 00:38:53.559
I am her biological mother.

00:38:53.840 --> 00:38:54.320
No way.

00:38:54.320 --> 00:38:56.679
I have to go fetch
my biological daughter.

00:38:56.840 --> 00:38:57.479
Mom,

00:38:57.479 --> 00:38:59.199
think carefully.

00:38:59.400 --> 00:39:01.559
The Shen family raised this girl.

00:39:01.560 --> 00:39:03.880
Shen Mingzhu never planned
to acknowledge her real parents.

00:39:03.880 --> 00:39:05.720
Now her parents suddenly appear.

00:39:05.920 --> 00:39:07.079
Can she handle it?

00:39:07.199 --> 00:39:08.469
Besides, she's living well.

00:39:08.470 --> 00:39:09.982
Why would she need to acknowledge you?

00:39:10.639 --> 00:39:10.960
This...

00:39:10.960 --> 00:39:12.119
What are you saying?

00:39:12.199 --> 00:39:14.320
We are her biological parents.

00:39:14.320 --> 00:39:14.679
Yes.

00:39:14.679 --> 00:39:16.519
Breaking bones affects the tendons too.

00:39:16.519 --> 00:39:18.519
This isn't up to her.

00:39:18.519 --> 00:39:20.119
The people who sent the girl away

00:39:20.119 --> 00:39:22.440
were us, right?

00:39:22.440 --> 00:39:22.960
Yes...

00:39:22.960 --> 00:39:24.639
The Shen family raised her with care,

00:39:24.639 --> 00:39:25.880
and did a good job.

00:39:25.880 --> 00:39:26.559
She grew up well.

00:39:26.559 --> 00:39:27.960
The family was happy together.

00:39:27.999 --> 00:39:30.559
Now we want to claim her?

00:39:30.720 --> 00:39:32.960
Even robbers wouldn't do this.

00:39:33.599 --> 00:39:34.199
Zhixia.

00:39:34.559 --> 00:39:35.639
I have a question.

00:39:36.639 --> 00:39:39.199
How can we prove
that our biological parents

00:39:39.199 --> 00:39:40.999
are Shen Mingzhu's biological parents?

00:39:41.280 --> 00:39:42.840
What nonsense is that?

00:39:43.440 --> 00:39:46.199
Location and time of giving the child,

00:39:46.519 --> 00:39:48.199
child's birth date,

00:39:48.199 --> 00:39:49.199
all match.

00:39:49.199 --> 00:39:50.880
Looks match too.

00:39:50.880 --> 00:39:52.400
But no solid proof.

00:39:53.920 --> 00:39:54.720
No solid...

00:39:54.720 --> 00:39:55.360
Wait.

00:39:55.999 --> 00:39:56.720
Zhixia.

00:39:57.360 --> 00:39:58.599
Call that little girl out.

00:39:58.999 --> 00:40:01.039
A paternity test will settle it.

00:40:01.039 --> 00:40:02.639
Once tested, we'll know.

00:40:02.720 --> 00:40:04.199
Paternity test, good idea.

00:40:04.199 --> 00:40:04.720
Right?

00:40:04.720 --> 00:40:05.920
Great idea.

00:40:06.400 --> 00:40:07.479
The problem is, why would

00:40:07.479 --> 00:40:09.679
Shen Mingzhu take a paternity test
with you?

00:40:10.119 --> 00:40:11.999
She'd be nice not to hate you.

00:40:11.999 --> 00:40:12.710
- No.
- Go away.

00:40:12.715 --> 00:40:13.630
We have no choice.

00:40:13.639 --> 00:40:15.840
This is all because of the old lady.

00:40:15.840 --> 00:40:17.159
No choice?

00:40:17.159 --> 00:40:18.440
How can you blame my mom?

00:40:18.440 --> 00:40:19.559
You say it's not her fault?

00:40:19.559 --> 00:40:20.240
Whose fault then?

00:40:20.240 --> 00:40:21.079
Yours.

00:40:21.079 --> 00:40:22.549
I'm in prison.

00:40:22.550 --> 00:40:24.004
Yes, because you're in prison,

00:40:24.048 --> 00:40:25.190
the child couldn't survive.

00:40:25.199 --> 00:40:27.440
Stop! All you do is argue!

00:40:29.199 --> 00:40:31.119
Why didn't you give me away back then?

00:40:31.119 --> 00:40:32.360
You were a bit older.

00:40:32.720 --> 00:40:34.159
Then you should have been given away.

00:40:34.440 --> 00:40:35.639
No one should stop me.

00:40:35.639 --> 00:40:37.679
I'm going to fetch my daughter.

00:40:37.679 --> 00:40:39.119
If you go now,

00:40:39.119 --> 00:40:40.199
my plan

00:40:40.199 --> 00:40:41.720
will be useless.

00:40:47.280 --> 00:40:48.039
Zhixia.

00:40:49.199 --> 00:40:50.039
Come.

00:40:50.039 --> 00:40:51.119
Yes, Zhixia.

00:40:51.199 --> 00:40:53.320
Hurry, sit down.

00:40:53.599 --> 00:40:54.360
Come, come.

00:40:56.360 --> 00:40:57.159
Zhixia.

00:40:57.960 --> 00:41:00.519
From now on, Mom and Dad won't argue.

00:41:00.519 --> 00:41:01.519
Won't argue.

00:41:01.519 --> 00:41:02.599
We'll listen to you.

00:41:02.679 --> 00:41:03.880
Yes, we'll listen to you.

00:41:07.039 --> 00:41:07.840
Zhixia.

00:41:08.440 --> 00:41:09.720
Got any good ideas?

00:41:10.039 --> 00:41:11.960
Tell Mom and Dad.

00:41:17.693 --> 00:41:18.630
Didn't Shen Mingzhu

00:41:18.639 --> 00:41:20.880
have her prenatal checkups
at the People's Hospital?

00:41:21.920 --> 00:41:25.199
I originally planned to give birth
at the Maternal and Child Hospital.

00:41:25.679 --> 00:41:28.599
Now I might as well transfer
to the People's Hospital.

00:41:28.720 --> 00:41:30.960
Our pregnancy timelines
are almost the same.

00:41:31.840 --> 00:41:33.039
I'll find an opportunity

00:41:33.039 --> 00:41:34.320
to get close to her.

00:41:34.760 --> 00:41:35.920
Gradually build a connection.

00:41:36.320 --> 00:41:37.479
Flirt indirectly.

00:41:38.880 --> 00:41:39.639
Good idea.

00:41:39.639 --> 00:41:40.280
Alright.

00:41:42.880 --> 00:41:43.880
Zhixia,

00:41:44.440 --> 00:41:45.280
well,

00:41:45.999 --> 00:41:49.039
how is Zhilu doing now?

00:41:49.360 --> 00:41:50.840
Is she living well?

00:41:50.840 --> 00:41:51.679
Well?

00:41:51.679 --> 00:41:55.559
Basically, as I had expected.

00:41:56.840 --> 00:41:58.199
"Zhilu" you mentioned...

00:41:58.440 --> 00:41:59.079
Zhilu.

00:41:59.079 --> 00:41:59.960
Shen Mingzhu.

00:42:01.079 --> 00:42:02.119
She's doing pretty well.

00:42:02.210 --> 00:42:04.180
She's been learning piano
since elementary school.

00:42:04.182 --> 00:42:05.630
Her awards cover the whole wall.

00:42:05.639 --> 00:42:06.550
Much better than me...

00:42:07.639 --> 00:42:09.199
Better than Xu Zhidong.

00:42:09.559 --> 00:42:10.989
She really is my daughter!

00:42:10.990 --> 00:42:12.848
Why don't you mention
that her husband died?

00:42:13.039 --> 00:42:14.199
Why bring me up?

00:42:14.248 --> 00:42:16.248
If you stay silent,
no one thinks you're mute.

00:42:22.999 --> 00:42:23.880
Mom.

00:42:23.880 --> 00:42:26.199
Her husband died,
and she can find another one.

00:42:27.039 --> 00:42:31.240
Why does this child
have such a hard life?

00:42:32.119 --> 00:42:32.720
Enough.

00:42:33.479 --> 00:42:34.079
Stop crying.

00:42:34.720 --> 00:42:35.760
I'm not dead.

00:42:55.100 --> 00:42:56.950
♪The world is noisy♪

00:42:57.550 --> 00:42:59.930
♪Turning around,
it's already a distant view♪

00:43:01.350 --> 00:43:03.230
♪Once I didn’t know what to do♪

00:43:03.230 --> 00:43:05.310
♪What to hold quietly♪

00:43:05.310 --> 00:43:08.260
♪Like a silent care♪

00:43:10.120 --> 00:43:12.530
♪Seasons pass by♪

00:43:12.530 --> 00:43:15.390
♪Time ticks away♪

00:43:15.880 --> 00:43:17.790
♪Seems like I understand a little♪

00:43:17.790 --> 00:43:19.570
♪And also let go of some things♪

00:43:19.570 --> 00:43:24.290
♪All the bittersweet flavors
are the essence of youth♪

00:43:24.290 --> 00:43:27.780
♪A long letter is written down♪

00:43:27.930 --> 00:43:31.410
♪Gently spreading love♪

00:43:31.610 --> 00:43:35.600
♪To all the forks in fate♪

00:43:35.600 --> 00:43:41.230
♪Loving all the moments
that deserve to be loved♪